	    <meta name="description" content="Marassi is the unrivaled coastal destination of Egypt's north coast; extending over 6.5 million sqm of impeccably-planned seaside indulgence. Featuring 5 beaches, 23 residential villages, 3300 hotel keys, an 18-hole golf course and one of the largest International Marinas in the Middle East; making it the North Coast's place to be." />
