<h1 class="wp-block-heading style=&quot;color:black&quot; has-black-color has-text-color">TOURIST YACHT VISA</h1>



<div style="height:45px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p style="font-size:16px">Great news for international yacht owners! Marassi Marina Yacht Club is excited to inform you that you now have the opportunity to submit your tourist yacht visit via the Maritime Transport Sector (MTS) website. This innovative process aims to simplify the acquisition of necessary approvals from authorities prior to your yacht&#8217;s arrival in Egypt. </p>



<p style="font-size:16px">Additionally, it streamlines the check-in procedure at Egyptian ports, saving you a whole day. Moreover, you can conveniently settle the check-in invoice directly on the website. For more details on how to submit your tourist yacht visit through MTS, we invite you to watch an informative guide video on the MTS Egypt website. Prepare for a hassle-free sailing experience!</p>



<a target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="https://www.mts.gov.eg/en/فيديو-استرشادى-للدخول-على-النافذه-الو/" title="SEE MORE" rel="noopener">SEE MORE</a>



<div style="height:27px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<div class="wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex"></div>
</div></div>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large margin-space-image"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1024" height="672" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20672'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-3357" data-lazy-srcset="https://www-marassimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Yacht-Visa-1024x672.jpg 1024w, https://www-marassimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Yacht-Visa-300x197.jpg 300w, https://www-marassimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Yacht-Visa-768x504.jpg 768w, https://www-marassimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Yacht-Visa.jpg 1200w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://www-marassimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Yacht-Visa-1024x672.jpg" /><noscript><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1024" height="672" src="https://www-marassimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Yacht-Visa-1024x672.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3357" srcset="https://www-marassimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Yacht-Visa-1024x672.jpg 1024w, https://www-marassimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Yacht-Visa-300x197.jpg 300w, https://www-marassimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Yacht-Visa-768x504.jpg 768w, https://www-marassimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Yacht-Visa.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></figure>
